  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Briony</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Briony_Joy_Hill_and_Lynora_Hill_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Briony Joy Hill and Lynora Hill by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Briony_Joy_Hill_and_Lynora_Hill_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/300px-Briony_Joy_Hill_and_Lynora_Hill_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Briony_Joy_Hill_and_Lynora_Hill_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/450px-Briony_Joy_Hill_and_Lynora_Hill_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Briony_Joy_Hill_and_Lynora_Hill_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/600px-Briony_Joy_Hill_and_Lynora_Hill_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Briony with <a href=\"/index.php/Joy_Hill\" title=\"Joy Hill\">Joy Hill</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lynora_Hill\" title=\"Lynora Hill\">Lynora Hill</a> by coldraindropsss</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_276_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">276&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Gerion_Lannister\" title=\"Gerion Lannister\">Gerion Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Joy_Hill\" title=\"Joy Hill\">Joy Hill</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (appendix)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Briony</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">common woman</a>. She is the mother of <a href=\"/index.php/Joy_Hill\" title=\"Joy Hill\">Joy Hill</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Gerion_Lannister\" title=\"Gerion Lannister\">Gerion Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafappendix:_lannister_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafappendix:_lannister_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Briony&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Briony\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Briony</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafappendix:_lannister_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafappendix:_lannister_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Appendix: Lannister Lineage.</span>\n</li>\n</ol>